(22643, 1, '2016-06-17 09:05:01', '2016-06-17 14:05:01', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Evea Ecofashion works with families Amazonian Peru based on the fair trade system, in a responsible, ethical and transparent, looking for the development of collecting and vegetable leather producing communities. Families articulate an integrated work, where tradition is passed down from father to son, involvement of the whole family where women contribute to the development of vegetable leather rugs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="22651" img_size="large" alignment="center"][vc_single_image][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Empowerment of families and fair trade', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22511-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-17 09:05:01', '2016-06-17 14:05:01', '', 22511, 'http://localhost/evea/22511-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(22644, 1, '2016-06-17 08:59:18', '2016-06-17 13:59:18', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1466171912888{padding-right: 2em !important;padding-left: 2em !important;}"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]The natural latex, also known as vegetable leather, for its resemblance to leather, is a rubber latex blanket with cotton. It is achieved by extracting shiringa latex trees, mixed with natural colorants and then smearing it on canvas streched cotton or steam drying. Is an ancient technique where trees aren´t cut down, only it removed the necesary latex for the tree to continue living and regenerated\n\nThe shiringa is a tree that grows up exclusive in the Amazon and it has inside a milky liquid call latex, when it is extracted and through artesanal proccess it has converted in latex and cotton blankets that is very similar to leather. Also call vegetable leather.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>"It is a very old technique where trees are not cut down, but the latex is extracted just enough for the tree alive and continue to regenerate".</strong></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="22464" img_size="large" alignment="center"][vc_single_image image="22646" img_size="large" alignment="center"][vc_single_image image="22647" img_size="large" alignment="center"][vc_single_image image="22648" img_size="large" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'What is the vegetable leather?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22502-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-17 08:59:18', '2016-06-17 13:59:18', '', 22502, 'http://localhost/evea/22502-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(22645, 1, '2016-06-17 09:12:24', '2016-06-17 14:12:24', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1466172663103{padding-right: 2em !important;padding-left: 2em !important;}"][vc_column width="2/3" css=".vc_custom_1466172602845{padding-right: 2em !important;padding-left: 2em !important;}"][vc_column_text]We know that ilegal and indiscriminate logging is the big problem of the Amazon. A year more than 150000 hectares of forest are deforested, either by illegal loggers, drug trafficking , etc. “ Amazon deforestation can alter the climate of the whole continent, rainfall patterns and cause serious droughts in some regions… If South America has the climate and the ecosystem it has, it is thanks to the Amazon…” (words Brazilian scientist Antonio Nobre)\n\nEvea Ecofashion, aware of this problem and valuable product that made these families and entrepreneurial communities, working with them to create clothing accesories such as wallets, handbags, bags, an others, offering an enviromentally friendly alternative in harmony with nature. In wich each bag developed by 2 or 3 trees are preserved, since each community has for use and protection , between 80 and 150 trees, covering an area of 300 hectares of preserved forest only for one family. Try to imagine if we can work with hundred of families.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>"Amazon deforestation can alter the climate of the whole continent, rainfall patterns and cause severe droughts".</strong></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Amazon forest conservation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22505-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-17 09:12:24', '2016-06-17 14:12:24', '', 22505, 'http://localhost/evea/22505-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
